  "texts": [
    "It employs a probabilistic approach to encode graph information effectively.",
    "VGAE consists of two essential components: an encoder and a decoder.",
    "The encoder utilizes a Graph Convolution Network (GCN) to transform graph nodes into a lower-dimensional latent space.",
    "It generates latent variables z i for each node by sampling from Gaussian distributions.",
    "These latent variables capture crucial structural information of the graph."
  ],
